Source: R/summarise_tracks.R
summarise_hatching_and_emergence_success.Rd

Utility to summarise a tibble of tracks with nest excavation data.

summarise_hatching_and_emergence_success(value)

Arguments

value

The output of parse_turtle_nest_encounters()

Details

Calculates:

  • count The count of nests

  • clutch_size_fresh Mean observed clutch size during nesting event

  • clutch_size_mean Mean of reconstructed clutch size

  • clutch_size_sd SD of reconstructed clutch size

  • clutch_size_min Min of reconstructed clutch size

  • clutch_size_maz Max of reconstructed clutch size

  • hatching_success_mean, sd, min, max Hatching success stats

  • emergence_success_mean, sd, min, max Emergence success stats
